(1. WORK DESCRIPTION) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(National Highways Authority of India \(NHAI\), Regional Office Karnataka & Goa,) Tj T*
(invites sealed tenders from eligible contractors for the following work:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Project Name: Four-Laning of NH-66 Panaji Udupi Section \(Package HC-03\)) Tj T*
(Chainage    : Km 182.000 to Km 231.600 \(49.6 km\), Karnataka) Tj T*
(Scope       : Earthwork, pavement construction \(WMM, DBM, BC\), drainage,) Tj T*
(              bridges \(3 Nos.\), culverts \(42 Nos.\), retaining walls,) Tj T*
(              road signage, safety barriers, and service roads.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Estimated Cost  : Rs. 4,50,00,00,000/- \(Rs. Four Hundred Fifty Crore\)) Tj T*
(EMD             : Rs. 90,00,000/- \(Rs. Ninety Lakh\) \(2% of estimated cost\)) Tj T*
(Tender Fee      : Rs. 25,000/- \(non-refundable, payable by DD\)) Tj T*
(Performance Security : 5% of contract value) Tj T*
(Defect Liability Period : 5 years) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. KEY DATES) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Publication of NIT              : 12 June 2026) Tj T*
(Last date for clarifications    : 25 June 2026) Tj T*
(Pre-Bid Meeting                 : 27 June 2026, 11:00 hrs at NHAI RO Bengaluru) Tj T*
(Last date for bid submission    : 15 July 2026, 17:00 hrs) Tj T*
(Opening of Technical Bids       : 17 July 2026, 11:00 hrs) Tj T*
(Bid validity period             : 180 days from date of submission) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(IMPORTANT: All eligibility criteria must be fulfilled as on the last date of) Tj T*
(bid submission. Non-fulfilment of any mandatory criterion shall lead to) Tj T*
(summary rejection of the bid.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
