(4.1 JV Eligibility) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(In case of a Joint Venture:) Tj T*
(  - Maximum 3 partners) Tj T*
(  - Lead member must hold at least 40% equity) Tj T*
(  - Lead member must individually meet 60% of all financial criteria) Tj T*
(  - Each JV partner must meet 25% of financial criteria individually) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.2 JV Restrictions) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  A firm may be member of only one JV bidding for this tender.) Tj T*
(  A firm participating as individual bidder cannot also be a JV partner.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
